🔗 [View Build](${buildInfo.buildUrl})""",

        'PIPELINE_FAILED': """
${baseMessage}

❌ *PIPELINE FAILED*
🔍 *Issue:* General pipeline failure
📄 *Details:* ${errorMessage}
🔧 *Action:* Check Jenkins logs for specific error details

🔗 [View Build](${buildInfo.buildUrl})""",

        'PIPELINE_UNSTABLE': """
${baseMessage}

⚠️ *PIPELINE UNSTABLE*
🔍 *Issue:* Pipeline completed with warnings
📄 *Details:* ${errorMessage}
🔧 *Action:* Review warnings in Jenkins logs

🔗 [View Build](${buildInfo.buildUrl})""",

        'PIPELINE_ABORTED': """
${baseMessage}

🛑 *PIPELINE ABORTED*
🔍 *Issue:* Pipeline was manually stopped or cancelled
